{"_path":"/knowledge/occult-knowledge","_dir":"knowledge","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Occult Knowledge","description":"","cat":"Base","id":"04","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"hidden-knowledge"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hidden Knowledge"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This knowledge is \"Occulted\", meaning it "},{"type":"element","tag":"s","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"is"}]},{"type":"text","value":" was \"Hidden\"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Derived from the Latin adjective "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Occultus"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" which means \"concealed, hidden from sight\", which is in turn derived from the Latin verb "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Occultare"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" which means \"to keep secret, to conceal.\" Just like in English, the word "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ocular"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" means \"related to the eye, related to sight\", which is derived from the Latin noun "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Oculus"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" meaning \"Eye\"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"mono","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Occult Knowledge is certain information that has been hidden from sight for a specific reason."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{"className":["desc"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Occult Knowledge constitutes both the Knowledge of "},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["font-bold","border-b"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Human Consciousness"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and how it operates, and the Knowledge of "},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"className":["font-bold","border-b"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Natural Law"}]},{"type":"text","value":", the unseen universal spiritual laws which govern the consequences of human behaviour."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In the ancient mystery traditions and occult schools, these concepts are known as the two ‘Arcana’ which translates to ‘Secret’ in both Latin and Greek (‘Arcanum (μυστικό)’ in Greek)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"minor-arcana"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Minor Arcana"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Lesser (Minor) Arcana: Hidden knowledge of the microcosm. – Deals with individual units of consciousness; the human psyche."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"major-arcana"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Major Arcana"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Greater (Major) Arcana: Hidden knowledge of the macrocosm – Understanding of the\nlarge (universal) laws of Nature that govern the macrocosm. → Natural Law,"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"hidden-knowledge","depth":2,"text":"Hidden Knowledge"},{"id":"minor-arcana","depth":2,"text":"Minor Arcana"},{"id":"major-arcana","depth":2,"text":"Major Arcana"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:1.knowledge:04.occult-knowledge.md","_source":"content","_file":"1.knowledge/04.occult-knowledge.md","_extension":"md"}